^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now we will discuss Boater's bid. I am all in favor of balancing. So in general Boater should not like us to play 1NT. However, balancing here is somewhat risky (although not totally out of line). And not vulnerable against vulnerable, balancing has some merit. |
